{
  "stem": "13313.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was always afraid that somebody was going to jump him, or attack him, or insult him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He knows from nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He has no fear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's oblivious.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm walking with these memories from, from 50 years before, exactly in those worst spots.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it did affect-- it did affect my feeling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was totally afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was watching around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was just waiting for someone to do something and for me to pounce.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, the point I was trying to make is-- and talk about coincidences-- and by the way, I told my son and the, and the children what happened here, and what happened on the pond and so forth.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it so happens, and this is almost unbelievable as a coincidence, that the place where my son and his kids stayed in 1994, which, by the way, this was the last time my mother saw them because she passed away six months later.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was a good thing that we went on that trip or she would never have seen the latest great grandson at the time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the address, that the apartment building attached to the hotel where my son, where my son stayed, that front door was exactly, exactly the same spot where in '44, 50 years earlier I had jumped that bully, the antisemitic bully, that had-- that, that, that had actually talked about sinking all the Jews in the sea.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That had to be my own son and their great grandchildren, grandchildren, would be exact in that same spot in a city of a million people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You can imagine the emotional feelings that I went through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was-- it was-- it was very traumatic.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
